{
  "title": "Water 4",
  "publicationStatus": "draft",
  "subtitle": "Confined and Unconfined Aquifers",
  "helpOnLoad": false,
  "aboutOnLoad": true,
  "about": [
    "In this model, you can explore the difference between confined and unconfined aquifers.",
    "",
    "Click the **Add well** button, and then move your cursor to where you want to drill a well.",
    "Click and hold until the well has reached the proper depth.",
    "",
    "Place one well into the unconfined aquifer.",
    "Adjust the **Rain probability** slider so that the water level in the unconfined aquifer remains steady.",
    "Then place one well into the confined aquifer.",
    "",
    "Use the graph to compare the water outputs of the different wells."
  ],
  "theme": ["has", "graph-title-bg", "standalone-playback", "no-slider-bar"],
  "aspectRatio": 1.5,
  "fontScale": 0.8,
  "models": [
    {
      "type": "iframe-model",
      "id": "iframe-model",
      "url": "models/lab-version/1/iframe-model/iframe-model.json",
      "modelOptions":{
        "url": "//models-resources.concord.org/agentscript/water/lab-embeddable.html#xMax=40",
        "template": "state/low-res/WaterModel-5-23-11-confinedAndUnconfined.json",
        "rainProbability": 0.4,
        "evapProbability": 20,
        "controls": {
          "wells": "removal",
          "remove": "well"
        }
      },
      "viewOptions": {
        "aspectRatio": 1.7,
        "controlButtons": "play_reset"
      },
      "onLoad": [
        "function disableComponents(value) {",
        "  setComponentDisabled('followRainButton', value);",
        "}",
        "disableComponents(true);",
        "onStart(function() { disableComponents(false); });",
        "onStop(function() { disableComponents(true); });"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "followRain",
      "initialValue": false,
      "onChange": [
        "// Note that we have to use .post() instead of method shortcuts, as this handler is",
        "// called before iframe can register its methods (before iframe communication is started).",
        "if (value) {",
        "  post('addRainSpotlight');",
        "  setComponentAttributes('followRainButton', {text: 'Stop following'});",
        "} else {",
        "  post('removeSpotlight');",
        "  setComponentAttributes('followRainButton', {text: 'Follow water droplet'});",
        "}"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [
    {
      "name": "year",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('month') / 12;"
    },
    {
      "name": "well1",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well1') || 0"
    },
    {
      "name": "well2",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well2') || 0"
    },
    {
      "name": "well3",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well3') || 0"
    },
    {
      "name": "well4",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well4') || 0"
    },
    {
      "name": "well5",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well5') || 0"
    }
  ],
  "helpTips": [
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "type": "playback",
      "id": "playback"
    },
    {
      "id": "followRainButton",
      "type": "button",
      "action": [
        "set('followRain', !get('followRain'));"
      ],
      "text": "Follow water droplet",
      "width": "14em"
    },
    {
      "id": "rainSlider",
      "type": "slider",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 1,
      "title": "Rain probability",
      "fillColor": "#459ACE",
      "width": "15em",
      "steps": 50,
      "labels": [
        {
          "value": "0",
          "label": "<i class='fa fa-sun-o' style='font-size: 1.5em; margin-right: 0.4em;'></i>"
        },
        {
          "value": "1",
          "label": "<i class='fa fa-umbrella' style='font-size: 1.5em;'></i>"
        }
      ],
      "property": "rainProbability"
    },
    {
      "id": "wells-graph",
      "type": "graph",
      "properties": [
        "well1",
        "well2",
        "well3",
        "well4",
        "well5"
      ],
      "enableZooming": false,
      "enableAxisScaling": false,
      "xProperty": "year",
      "title": "Well Output",
      "titlePosition": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "100%",
      "xlabel": "Time (years)",
      "xmin": 0,
      "xmax": 10,
      "ylabel": "Well output",
      "ymin": 0,
      "ymax": 600,
      "xTickCount": 6,
      "yTickCount": 6,
      "xFormatter": "d",
      "yFormatter": ".2r",
      "dataColors": [
        "#0000FF",
        "#FF0066",
        "#000000",
        "#CC33FF",
        "#FF6600"
      ],
      "legendLabels": [
        "Well 1",
        "Well 2",
        "Well 3",
        "Well 4",
        "Well 5"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "template": [
    {
      "id": "right",
      "left": "model.right",
      "width": "model.width * 0.6",
      "top": "model.top",
      "bottom": "model.bottom",
      "padding": "0 0.5em"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottom",
      "top": "model.bottom",
      "left": "model.left",
      "margin-top": "0.3em"
    }
  ],
  "layout": {
    "bottom": [
      ["playback"],
      ["followRainButton"],
      ["rainSlider"]
    ],
    "right": [
      "wells-graph"
    ]
  }
}
